<!DOCTYPE html>

<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>约饭</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="onepage">
      <div class="onepage-bg" id="onepage">  </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="title-text">
            <div class="col-md-12 headfontsize">
              <h1 class="headh1content">
                一顿饭，创造一段新关系
              </h1>
              <p> 用餐廳、話題、興趣...等資訊，來尋找跟你志同道合的朋友一起吃飯吧！</p>
              <p class="btn-app-store">
                 <%= link_to("发起约饭", new_post_path(@post), class: "btn btn-danger btn-lg", style: "background-color:#f01d67;") %>
              </p>

              <form class="subForm" id="dinnerSearchForm">
                 <div class="search_container">
                    <input type="text" class="search" name="search" placeholder="搜尋飯局關鍵字">
                    <a href="javascript:;" class="clear_btn"><i class="fa fa-times"></i></a>
                </div>
                    <input type="submit" class="submit" value="搜尋">
            	</form>




            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  <div class="twopage">

    <div class="container">
      <div class="row ">

       <% @posts.each do |post| %>
         <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="img">
              <%= link_to post_path(post) do %>
                <% if post.image.present? %>
                    <%= image_tag(post.image.thumb.url, class: "thumbnail") %>
                <% else %>
                    <%= image_tag("http://placehold.it/200x200&text=No Pic", class: "thumbnail") %>
                <% end %>
                <div class="desc">
                  <h1> <%= post.title %> </h1>
                  <h3> <strong> <%= post.eat_venue %> </strong></h3>
                  <h3><strong> <%= post.eat_day %> </strong></h3>
               </div>
             <% end %>
           </div>
         </div>
      <% end %>
     </div>
    </div>

      <div class="twopagebtn">
        <a id="twopage-easy" href="#" class="btn btn-success btn-lg"> 载入更多约饭 </a>
      </div>
    </div>


  <div class="threepage">
    <div class="threepage-bg" id="threepage">
      <div class="threepagecontent">
        <div class="threepagetext">
         <h3>「Eatgether一起吃」利用聚餐交友功能，徹底結合「飲食」與「社交」，為餐廳創造無限的可能性！
           <br><br>只等有缘的你
          </h3>
        </div>
       </div>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
          <div class="threepage-weixin">
            <a href="#">
               <img src="http://ww1.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t19or41kj3069069wec.jpg" style="width: 100px;" >
            </a>
         </div>
       </div>

       <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
         <div class="threepage-weixin">
           <a href="#">
              <img src="http://ww2.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t19oq9rvj3069069jrf.jpg" style="width: 100px;">
           </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="bottompage col-md-4 ">
        <div class="threepage-weixin">
          <a href="#">
             <img src="http://ww3.sinaimg.cn/large/006tNc79jw1f9t2mm8664j305o05odfq.jpg" style="width: 100px;">
          </a>
       </div>
      </div>

     </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  </body>
</html>
